<node id="CSCE 670 Information Storage And Retrieval Core Concepts">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Information Storage And Retrieval Core Concepts</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This core topic of CSCE 670 covers the representation, storage, and access to very large multimedia document collections.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Fundamental Data Structures And Algorithms">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Fundamental Data Structures And Algorithms</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic covers the fundamental data structures and algorithms essential for information storage and retrieval systems in CSCE 670.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Retrieval Systems Design And Evaluation">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Retrieval Systems Design And Evaluation</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic in CSCE 670 includes techniques for designing and evaluating complete retrieval systems, along with algorithms for indexing, compressing, and querying large collections.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Web Search Concepts And Models">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Web Search Concepts And Models</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic in CSCE 670 covers key concepts for web search, such as text indexing, retrieval models, evaluation, Web crawling, link-based algorithms (e.g., PageRank), and learning to rank.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Recommender Systems Concepts And Models">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Recommender Systems Concepts And Models</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic in CSCE 670 covers key concepts for recommender systems, such as collaborative filtering, matrix factorization, evaluation, and implicit recommendation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Algorithm Design Implementation And Evaluation">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Algorithm Design Implementation And Evaluation</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic focuses on designing, implementing, and evaluating core algorithms for web search and recommendation systems as a learning objective of CSCE 670.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Recent Research Application">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Recent Research Application</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic involves identifying salient features and applying recent research results in web search and recommender systems, including adversarial information retrieval, as taught in CSCE 670.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Define Web Search Concepts And Models Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Define Web Search Concepts And Models Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completing CSCE 670, learners will be able to define and explain key concepts and models relevant to web search.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Define Recommender Systems Concepts And Models Outcome">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Define Recommender Systems Concepts And Models Outcome</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completing CSCE 670, learners will be able to define and explain key concepts and models relevant to recommender systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Information Retrieval Techniques Course">
  <data key="d0">Information Retrieval Techniques Course</data>
  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">A course covering various topics in information retrieval, including Boolean models, vector space models, recommender systems, and large language models for ranking, with a structured schedule of assignments, quizzes, and a group project, and specific academic policies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f5841d5517bdecb50ee7c2b009ce2a8c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753089</data>
