  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">A general policy concerning late submissions, where makeup work for an excused absence is not considered late and is exempt from the policy.&lt;SEP&gt;The Late Work Policy is a general rule that defines how makeup work for an excused absence is handled, exempting it from being considered late.&lt;SEP&gt;This policy states that makeup work for excused absences is exempt from late penalties, referencing Student Rule 7.</data>
