  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">The official rules and conditions governing the administration of makeup exams, primarily for students with excused absences.&lt;SEP&gt;This policy outlines the conditions under which makeup exams may be granted, generally only for excused absences with documentation, and states that makeup exams will differ from the original exams.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa849f6a630caef4a2ea4121e93715e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d55a5c42258b138ee2fec076c197b5fc</data>
