<node id="Instructor">
  <data key="d0">Instructor</data>
  <data key="d1">instructor</data>
  <data key="d2">The teaching professional who students must contact as soon as possible with documentation if an excused absence is expected.&lt;SEP&gt;The person responsible for teaching the course, who students must contact for excused absences and rescheduling, and who has discretion over incomplete grades.&lt;SEP&gt;The person in this course who reserves the right to define makeup work for an excused absence.&lt;SEP&gt;The primary academic staff member leading the course.&lt;SEP&gt;The instructor is responsible for making class announcements via the mailing list for CSCE Compiler Fall 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;The instructor for CSCE Compiler Fall 2025 is responsible for class announcements, encouraging collaboration, and enforcing academic policies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-daa849f6a630caef4a2ea4121e93715e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d55a5c42258b138ee2fec076c197b5fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12f7de51d4f4e2342bdef5b2b88af321&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61707c7d1df4b793e9891ac27b929204&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5d9487684237fd973d101db9ba5ac8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43473e1e2732247c26a0d5c3140658f</data>
