  <data key="d1">communicationchannel</data>
  <data key="d2">Email is a communication channel that is explicitly stated as not acceptable for regrading requests.&lt;SEP&gt;A communication channel that should be considered a last resort for questions, after Campuswire, in-class discussions, or office hours.</data>
