<node id="Incomplete Grade Policy">
  <data key="d0">Incomplete Grade Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">This policy governs the assignment of incomplete grades, specifying that they are given only for authorized absences or causes beyond a student's control, based on Student Rule 10, and are at the instructor's discretion.</data>
