<node id="Student">
  <data key="d0">Student</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An individual enrolled in the course who is subject to all academic policies regarding exams, grades, and absences.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual enrolled in the course, subject to its policies and using its resources.&lt;SEP&gt;Students are individuals taking the CSCE Compiler Fall 2025 course, required to have a webcam for quizzes, and can utilize university resources.&lt;SEP&gt;An individual enrolled in the course, responsible for completing assignments and adhering to academic policies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d55a5c42258b138ee2fec076c197b5fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0bfffd3b3a70fa19e5adadca39073ad8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5d9487684237fd973d101db9ba5ac8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43473e1e2732247c26a0d5c3140658f</data>
