  <data key="d0">Submission of Assignments and Grade Posting Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">This policy dictates that all assignments must be submitted electronically via Gradescope and specifies how grades are posted to Canvas.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Assignment Deadlines and Late Penalty Policy">
  <data key="d0">Assignment Deadlines and Late Penalty Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">This policy sets established deadlines for assignments, allows late submissions with an incurred penalty, and specifies conditions for non-acceptance outside grace periods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Project Assignments Late Policy">
  <data key="d0">Project Assignments Late Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">academicpolicy</data>
  <data key="d2">This policy details the allowance of late submission for project assignments, including a 39-hour grace period for non-"hard-deadline" projects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Canvas">
  <data key="d0">Canvas</data>
  <data key="d1">platform</data>
  <data key="d2">Canvas is the platform where final assignment scores, imported from Gradescope, are posted.&lt;SEP&gt;A learning management system that is explicitly stated not to be the main communication or Q&amp;A platform for the class.&lt;SEP&gt;Canvas is an online platform that is specifically noted as not being used for class announcements by the instructor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5d9487684237fd973d101db9ba5ac8b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a43473e1e2732247c26a0d5c3140658f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Autograder">
  <data key="d0">Autograder</data>
  <data key="d1">software</data>
  <data key="d2">The autograder is a component of Gradescope that processes submissions, and students are advised against using it as a primary debugging tool.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="Grace Period">
  <data key="d0">Grace Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A defined timeframe, specifically 39 hours for project assignments in this course, during which late submissions are allowed without immediate penalty. Course staff will not answer assignment questions during this period.&lt;SEP&gt;A grace period is a specified duration following an assignment deadline during which late submissions are accepted, typically without course staff support.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12f7de51d4f4e2342bdef5b2b88af321</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="University Approved Absences">
  <data key="d0">University Approved Absences</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Absences officially sanctioned by the university which allow for exceptions to late work submission rules outside of grace periods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-aa73fee78ff788a909465d0d4489187a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774753300</data>
  <data key="d6" />
