  <data key="d1">course</data>
  <data key="d2">This is the course, identified by its mailing list, for which various academic policies, resources, and communication methods are described.&lt;SEP&gt;This course involves compiler design and is scheduled for Fall 2025, where students are expected to spend 3 hours per week outside of class per credit hour.</data>
