  <data key="d1">platform</data>
  <data key="d2">Campuswire is a communication platform that course staff will not check during the last 6 hours before a deadline.&lt;SEP&gt;The designated main communication and Q&amp;A platform for the class, replacing Canvas for this purpose.&lt;SEP&gt;Campuswire is a platform designated for class announcements and student discussions in CSCE Compiler Fall 2025, described as "For You and By You."</data>
