<node id="CSCE 605 Course Content">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 605 Course Content</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">The course covers advanced topics in compiler writing, parser generators and compiler-compilers, dynamic storage and scope resolution, data flow analysis, and code optimization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f3f1b6a84ddcd0ca67ec8a38fa0ccdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
