  <data key="d0">CSCE 638 Learning Outcome 3</data>
  <data key="d1">learningoutcome</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon completion of CSCE 638, learners will be able to apply established techniques and propose practical methods and solutions to tackle challenges in natural language processing.</data>
